RIGOL product online upgrade service terms

RIGOL product online upgrade service is a software upgrade service for users remotely via the Internet.。

In order to ensure the smooth progress of the online upgrade process, it is necessary to network and collect and process the following local information:

  • Device information, including model number, serial number, hardware version number, logical version number, software version number, MAC address, IP
  • Device status, including power running status, hardware module running status, critical component working status, available storage size, current device boot status definition, custom function

By clicking Agree, you have read and fully agree to the contents of the above terms and the RIGOL Privacy Policy, and are willing to accept all the above terms and restrictions of RIGOL's Privacy Policy, and begin to provide online software upgrade services for you.
